66
00:03:33,627 --> 00:03:34,765
And I lost everything.

67
00:03:34,895 --> 00:03:36,772
My uncle, he said to me,
"You and I are going

68
00:03:36,897 --> 00:03:37,967
to make a lot of
money together,"

69
00:03:38,132 --> 00:03:40,271
