71
00:03:42,803 --> 00:03:44,009
if I remember,
back in my childhood.

72
00:03:44,171 --> 00:03:45,650
And it was called
Alice's Restaurant,

73
00:03:45,806 --> 00:03:47,513
and then we went into
nightclubs and we opened

74
00:03:47,674 --> 00:03:48,880
about four or five
nightclubs.

75
00:03:49,042 --> 00:03:52,114
It became very big
